name: Phiskate
description:
Play as a Phiskater cruising through a neon city with beautiful music while you make your way to your destiny by performing a variety of tricks on several interesting configurations.

Use SPACE BAR to perform every trick.

This game was made from scratch in seven days for the Boundless Game Jam.

If you want to hear to full soundtrack you can check out my youtube channel Treemolo GameDev. I post there all the official tracks I composed.

This is the playlist with the OST I composed: Phiskate OST by Treemolo
